text: Zumholz was a municipality in the district Sense in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. On 1 January 2017, Zumholz and Oberschrot became part of Plaffeien.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz accessed 10 January 2017 == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Former municipalities of Fribourg
